Nigerian rapper, Naetochukwu Chikwe, popularly known as Naeto C on Wednesday celebrated his mother as she turned 75. The excited son took to his Instagram page on Wednesday night to share pictures of his mum, accompanied with a short yet heartfelt message. In the message, the rapper said that he thanked God every day for her and also celebrated her daily too. He also professed love to his mother whom he affectionately called “beautiful babe.” “Today my beautiful babe turns 75! I celebrate you and thank God everyday for you, my amazing mum. I love you! #SweetMother #Igolo, ” the rapper wrote. See post below:  Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com